comment: Dragic (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position as he contests Payton's (ORL) drive and shot attempt.
Wade (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Payton's (ORL) drive and shot attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) legally contests Wade's (MIA) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.

Fournier (ORL) commits a take foul on Wade (MIA).
Miami commits a 24 second shot clock violation.
